defaultIntroduction
defaultDr Jennifer Colman is registered and licensed with the GMC. She was an elected medical member of the GMC, for the English constituency, from 27 April 2000 to 30 June 2003 and also a charity trustee of the organisation. She has also been called to the Bar and holds licensed access from the BSB. 
