default“It is also plain that so serious a sanction taken against a professional individual as erasure from the medical record is of such a nature that, if injustice was done, however long ago, it is time that it was remedied. Delay cannot be an excuse for failing to do that. None of the delay, it seems has arisen as a result of the fault of the applicant.”   
